HEADWORD: Myrmicine
<hw>Myr"mi*cine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to <gen>Myrmica</gen>, a genus of ants including
the small house ant (<spn>Myrmica molesta</spn>), and many
others.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

